4.10	The_Almost_Moon	The Almost Moon	The Almost Moon is the third book and second novel by American writer Alice Sebold, author of her memoir, Lucky and The Lovely Bones. It was released by Little, Brown and Company in the United States on October 16, 2007.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/0/0a/The_Almost_Moon_%28Alice_Sebold_novel%29_cover_art.jpg/200px-The_Almost_Moon_%28Alice_Sebold_novel%29_cover_art.jpg
